<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title><%= assigns[:page_title] || "CapsensQonto · Phoenix Framework" %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/css/app.css") %>"/>
    <%= csrf_meta_tag() %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <section class="container">
        <nav role="navigation">
        </nav>
      </section>
    </header>
    <main role="main" class="container">
      <%= if get_flash(@conn, :info) do %>
        <span class="flash d-none info"><%= get_flash(@conn, :info) %></span>
      <% end %>
      <%= if get_flash(@conn, :error) do %>
        <span class="flash d-none error"><%= get_flash(@conn, :error) %></span>
      <% end %>

      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center my-3">
          <div class="col-6 text-center">
            <h2>Intégrez Qonto à Slack en 2 min</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row justify-content-center my-3">
          <div class="col-8 text-center">
            <h4>Ce site vous permet d'envoyer vos flux financiers Qonto (entrant et/ou sortant) dans un channel Slack</h4>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row justify-content-center my-5">
          <div class="col-12">
            <h3>
              <svg class="bi bi-lock-fill" width="0.8em" height="0.8em" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <rect width="11" height="9" x="2.5" y="7" rx="2"/>
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.5 4a3.5 3.5 0 117 0v3h-1V4a2.5 2.5 0 00-5 0v3h-1V4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              Le site est totalement sécurisé et respecte vos données personnelles. Son code est opensource consultable ici : mettre le lien</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <%= render @view_module, @view_template, assigns %>

        <div class="row justify-content-center my-5">
          <div class="col-12">
            <h4 class="text-center">
              Made with
              <svg class="bi bi-heart-fill" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8 1.314C12.438-3.248 23.534 4.735 8 15-7.534 4.736 3.562-3.248 8 1.314z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              by <%= link("CapSens", to: "https://capsens.eu/") %> l'agence web des fintechs
            </h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/js/app.js") %>"></script>
  </body>
</html>
